-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Arcelormittal, ASOS, Novartis, Total 
-- 
-- Mon Jun 09, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



June 9 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Arcelormittal, ASOS and Novartis, on Monday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Aggreko PLC <AGGK.L>: Panmure cuts to hold from buy rating * Arcelormittal SA <ISPA.AS>: S&P Capital IQ raises to hold from sell rating * Johnson Matthey <JMAT.L>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral rating  * Novartis <NOVN.VX>: Barclays raises to equalweight from underweight * Total <TOTF.PA>: Canaccord Genuity cuts to hold from buy rating  Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Monday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* 3I Group <III.L>: Barclays raises price target to 485p from 430p; rating overweight * Acciona <ANA.MC>: HSBC cuts to underweight from neutral; raises target to 58 euros from 51 * Aggreko PLC <AGGK.L>: Panmure cuts to hold from buy rating * Aquarius <AQP.L>: Panmure cuts to hold from buy; target price to 23p from 43p  * Arcelormittal SA <ISPA.AS>: S&P Capital IQ raises to hold from sell; target to 12.10 euros * ASOS <ASOS.L>: Jefferies cuts target price to 5,700p from 6,200p; rating buy  * ASOS <ASOS.L>: Liberum cuts price target to 1440p from 2500p; rating sell  * Banco Popular <POP.MC>: JP Morgan raises to overweight from neutral  * Banco Popular <POP.MC>: SocGen revises target price to 6.6 euros from 6.3 euros; buy * BME <BME.MC>: Citigroup raises price target to 34.50 euros from 19 euros; rating neutral * BT Group PLC <BT.L>: Citigroup raises price target to 450p from 430p; rating buy  * Burckhardt Compression <BCHN.S>: UBS cuts target price to Sfr 510 from Sfr 520; rating buy * C&C Group <GCC.I>: JP Morgan raises target price to 4.50 euros from 4.25 euros; neutral * Continental <CONG.DE>: Barclays raises price target to 195 euros from 186 euros;overweight * Italcementi <ITAI.MI>: Bernstein revises target to 7.30 euros from 8 euros; market-perform * Hikma Pharmaceuticals <HIK.L>: Barclays raises price target to 1890p from 1750p;overweight * Johnson Matthey <JMAT.L>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral rating  * Kcom Group <KCOM.L>: Oriel raises to hold from sell rating  * Lonmin PLC <LMI.L>: Panmure cuts price target to 339p from 420p; rating buy * Lonza Group <LONN.VX>: JP Morgan raises target price to Sfr 103 from Sfr 80; neutral  * Novartis <NOVN.VX>: Barclays raises to equalweight from underweight;target to Sfr 81  * Rushydro <HYDR.MM>: JP Morgan cuts to underweight from neutral  * Smiths Group <SMIN.L>: Barclays cuts price target to 1190p from 1240p; rating underweight * Total <TOTF.PA>: Canaccord Genuity cuts to hold from buy rating